  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The biomarker study adds to our previous study on biomarkers in tear fluid. In this study the
      investigators examine wether the biomarker levels are in correlation with the disease level
      and duration of disease.

      The questionnaire study focuses on the patients perspective. With a validated questionnaire
      fore keratoconus patient it examine the patients self.-evaluated visual challenges and
      quality of life
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
